item.title: Cudelice Brazelton IV: Tensors | Cell Project Space
item.description: The multimedia artist Cudelice Brazelton IV was born in Dallas and studied in Germany, where he now lives. The notes for this show, Brazelton’s first in London, state he spent some time in between “working in Ohio’s industrial foundries”. That sounds like, but doesn’t quite explicitly state, that he had a job in a factory. Or maybe it was a fancy art residency. Either way, the sounds and sights of the factory floor are clearly a major inspiration.
